metadata.description:
The Wizards of Ether collection is a high quality animated project created by a pixel art god aiming to not only showcase one of the coolest aesthetics but to spark pleasant magical spells and surprises after mint. Only 999 will ever exist in this genesis collection with the most fun and interesting burn mechanism to reduce the genesis token count.
The community will be made up of loyal wizards who put their fellow wizards first, ahead of any personal gains.
metadata.name: Wizards of Ether #1
